entries.arrived_at_loc: You have arrived at the intercept coordinates. I hope you're as good as I think, this will get rough.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.first_attack: Here they come! May the force be with you pilot, you will need it...
entries.found_loc: Uploaded intercept coordinates to your nav computer. Hurry there pilot, our fighters are all busy guarding their assigned routes!
entries.mission_complete: Amazing, I didn't think you could do it. Get out of there, we are safe in this nebula for now.
entries.outofrange: Rebel Fleet Command: < You are moving too far away from the intercept coordinates, bombers will slip through! >
entries.outofrange_failed: Rebel Fleet Command: < The fighters are upon us, you let them slip through! We are under atta.. >
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: The fleet is starting its relocation. They will need approximately ten minutes to reach safety. Hang in there and good luck pilot!
entries.quest_location_d: The Endor system is still mostly uncharted to us but we have managed to find a nebula that we hope to hide our fleet in while they are repairing.
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: You are at the correct coordinates. Don't let any Imperial ships get through you to the fleet.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Fleet Command: < A straggling freighter of ours are arriving out our old location. You need to get over there and escort him to us without being detected. >
entries.title: Endor system: Prevent Imperial fighters from reaching the fleet in the Endor system.
entries.title_d: Our fleet in the Endor system has been spotted and the Empire is sending fighters and bombers our way! We are trying to fight them off but are spread out too thin. You are assigned a sector to protect from any Imperial ships passing through while our fleet move to a new hiding spot. Hurry!
entries.trans_update: Tactical Computer: < %DI percent of the fleet has escaped in to the nebula. >
entries.transmission_received: Rebel Fleet Command: < Almost the entire fleet are in the nebula, hold out for just a few more seconds pilot! >
entries.transmission_start: Rebel Fleet Command: < We are moving in to a nearby nebula to hide. We need ten minutes! >
